Package de.jannlab.tools

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClassificationValidator
    This class allows to simply evaluate classification tasks.
    DataTools
    This class provides some helper methods for data handling.
    Debug
    This class provides Methods for handling String containing lines, which can be used for debugging tasks.
    DefaultNetTrainerListener
    This class implements a standard NetTrainerListener, which just prints out the validation error over time.
    EvaluationTools
    This class provides some helper methods, to keep the code corresponding to experiments simple.
    NetTools
    This class contains common methods for handling net instance.
    RegressionValidator
    This class allows to simply evaluate regression tasks.
